    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about that before you inquire. The exterior shows considerable wear \u2014 expect multiple scratches, paint chips, dents, and fading throughout. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general neglect visible throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues and may require significant repairs to be reliably road-worthy; it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone looking for parts, or a mechanically experienced individual who can address the underlying problems. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly.",
