      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and represents a solid, dependable used car purchase. The exterior shows some light surface scratches and minor wear consistent with normal use, but there are no significant dents or structural damage. The paint retains good color and shine with only minor blemishes upon close inspection. The interior is well-maintained with some expected wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, major stains, or broken components. All major mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are functioning properly, and the car drives smoothly. It has been regularly maintained and is ready for daily driving. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged. Priced fairly at $34,000 to reflect its honest good condition.",
